%% Control One Compliance Scan Sequence
sequenceDiagram
    participant Scheduler as Agent Scheduler
    participant Agent as Node Agent
    participant API as Control Plane API
    participant Queue as Worker Queue
    participant Worker as Worker Executor
    participant Evidence as Evidence Store
    participant UI as Web UI (React)

    Scheduler->>Agent: Trigger scheduled compliance scan
    Agent->>API: POST /api/v1/jobs {type: compliance, results payload}
    API-->>Agent: 202 Accepted + Job ID
    API->>Queue: Enqueue compliance job
    activate Queue
    Queue->>Worker: Deliver job for execution
    deactivate Queue
    activate Worker
    Worker->>Evidence: Persist compliance artifacts (S3/Blob)
    Worker->>API: Update job status (running -> succeeded/failed) with metadata
    deactivate Worker
    API-->>UI: Updated compliance dashboard via polling/stream
    UI->>Operator: Surface pass/fail, remediation hooks
